Description.SourceString: A radio bunker that provides intel to friendly units about the surrounding area. It is capable of increased effectiveness, and is equipped with binoculars that give occupants a greater field of view.
Description.LocalizedString: A radio bunker that provides intel to friendly units about the surrounding area. Reinforced with wood, it can withstand more punishment than a standard radio tower, and therefore is capable of increased effectiveness.
